Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.86,0:00:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南方的宇宙散发青色的光辉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.47,0:00:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是二次冲击的光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.67,0:00:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌上人类未来的浩瀚任务
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.94,0:00:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,横跨180年的大作战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在是西元2356年12月19日
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仰望天际 满天繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.26,0:00:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞往通向明日的灿烂大道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥抱内心的蓝天 go far way
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.02,0:01:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,习惯了总是羡慕别人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.42,0:01:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,值得自豪的自己逐渐远去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.20,0:01:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍动无形之翼 我们展翅高飞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.24,0:01:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生而为人因此能描绘梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.34,0:01:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仰望天际 满天繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.45,0:01:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞往通向明日的灿烂大道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.25,0:01:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥抱内心的蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.06,0:01:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要跟你在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.23,0:01:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将能摆脱懦弱的自己奔驰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.03,0:01:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来请无限延伸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.03,0:01:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,go far way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.40,0:02:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(220,160)\fs22\shad0}第１０话  欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.28,0:02:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叙事诗基地狄托洛司令的留言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.19,0:02:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是米盖尔？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.92,0:02:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织原 你那边状况如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次结束之后过来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.69,0:02:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们来讨论明年的运动会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.46,0:02:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过下次会是我们赢的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.77,0:02:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二次冲击还有一分钟抵达
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始进行倒数
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,57 56 55 54…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.19,0:02:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在可说是即将接触的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有30秒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.49,0:02:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,28 27 26 25 24…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.47,0:02:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有10秒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8 7 6…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.48,0:03:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:09.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二次冲击来临了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有系统正常运作中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲击吸收率100％
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.40,0:03:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作战成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.40,0:03:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.38,0:03:40.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 志麻
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.75,0:03:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就只要等待它通过就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.46,0:03:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.13,0:03:54.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.86,0:03:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.14,0:04:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报告现状
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩瀚长城没事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在以105％能量运作中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.98,0:04:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过有多数物体突破
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告知所有飞行机编队
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始进入迎击行动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展现日常成果的时候到了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护能量产生装置
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说浩瀚长城\N根据计算是不会被突破吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.18,0:05:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「事实比小说还离奇」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.38,0:05:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这么说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.25,0:05:25.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这是展现身手的机会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.39,0:05:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GO！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任务的进行状况
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.77,0:05:39.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又入侵主伺服器？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.27,0:05:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次真的会被退学喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多东西突破进来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过因撞上护罩时速度降低
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.21,0:05:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且体积都很小
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前飞行机队似乎都能完全处置
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.92,0:05:55.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小碰他们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.22,0:06:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片濑 过来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.86,0:06:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片濑 不要发呆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.67,0:06:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快张开护罩\N不然会被打到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 志麻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光太…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,0:06:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是0304 推进机损毁了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.46,0:06:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法操纵 无法操纵！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.63,0:06:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陨石进入冲撞轨道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.20,0:06:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-危险！\N-无法回避 无法回避
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志麻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以 片濑！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片濑座机损伤？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.29,0:07:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-等一下 冷静下来\N-发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.35,0:07:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-借我看一下 看不到啦\N-小碰没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像只是机体擦伤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.86,0:07:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光太已经要带她回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.93,0:07:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去接小碰回来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.11,0:07:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舰内系统恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害状况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲击波本身被浩瀚长城挡下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害都是来自小型陨石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:43.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正确认对地上的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.03,0:07:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过L4有一台\NL5有两台装置撞到陨石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.33,0:07:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有几个人受伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.90,0:07:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好几个陨石落到月面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.47,0:07:55.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过地底都市没有损害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.34,0:08:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月球周围的飞行机队\N调一半到其他据点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来应该能撑过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不再发生状况的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片濑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片濑！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.37,0:08:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片濑 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有受伤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.25,0:08:39.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碰 光太！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:45.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这个地方做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.15,0:08:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碰！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.12,0:08:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.39,0:08:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 你活得很好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.40,0:08:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我担心死了 片濑志麻！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.40,0:08:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽莎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.27,0:09:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.01,0:09:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为我很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.51,0:09:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是都做得不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没做什么就被带回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.30,0:09:31.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小碰…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说这什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不但救了驾驶员同伴\N而且还平安回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.54,0:09:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做得很好 片濑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.41,0:09:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺起胸膛来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师偶尔也会说好话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.68,0:09:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说的都是好话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常你们也该听进去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.69,0:09:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好乖好乖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司…司令！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事情了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.28,0:10:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巨大陨石的直径约100公里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,位于会撞上地球的轨道上！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.89,0:11:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可抵达范围内的飞行机\N全部进行攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得无济于事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.78,0:11:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方太巨大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度的能源炮根本没用
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.51,0:11:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去会一直线飞向地球
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经无计可施了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞行机的火力完全无效
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.56,0:11:36.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不可能破坏目标
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.79,0:11:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L4有三台 L5有两台\N能量装置遭陨石冲撞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.43,0:11:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩瀚长城强度开始降低
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令 防护罩的洞太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.83,0:11:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩瀚长城的平衡遭到破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.54,0:11:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去的话\N浩瀚长城将会完全魔溃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.68,0:11:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.71,0:11:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定还有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定还有其他的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.55,0:12:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陨石跟护罩的洞都太大\N飞行机根本无计可施
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.19,0:12:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无计可施…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.69,0:12:11.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那会变成什么样子呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.69,0:12:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陨石会毁灭地球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到护罩损毁之后
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮 殖民地跟我们都会完蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.10,0:12:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们会死掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.28,0:12:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.72,0:12:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果用那个的话或许可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.52,0:12:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要用那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.09,0:12:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那个的威力的确可以
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:49.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过要出动必须先行准备
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.27,0:12:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令 学园方面有紧急连络
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学园？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.51,0:13:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是要全部拿掉是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本没有意义呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.15,0:13:06.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.25,0:13:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是地球放在这边的大家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.02,0:13:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让这个巨大玩偶可以动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.75,0:13:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它全身都有重力能量产生装置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要全部启动的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.39,0:13:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许就可以封住护罩的洞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白银
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边刚好在想同样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.67,0:13:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过问题在准备时间跟人手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.27,0:13:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操纵系统也还没调整吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.07,0:13:34.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操纵系统已依照机能\N分成双人机型了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要再十分钟就能成为\N最底限但能使用的状态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.95,0:13:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修塔老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.55,0:13:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那驾驶员呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.29,0:13:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我们来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.79,0:13:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.05,0:13:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预科生音山光太
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有片濑志麻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你们还是预科生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.69,0:13:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有驾驶员都出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫他们回来的话会来不及
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.47,0:14:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把地球的命运交给孩子们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.94,0:14:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这条路了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只是一点点的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.07,0:14:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也必须要赌下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.08,0:14:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请相信学生们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.21,0:14:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有犹豫的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.98,0:14:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去负责那边的控制系统
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备出动无限号！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 获得许可了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.73,0:14:27.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快作业 没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.64,0:14:36.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无限号专用的能源炮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.01,0:14:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.11,0:14:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放在三号货柜里\N让无限号装备这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这个破坏那颗巨大陨石
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:47.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用手册在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 这就是最后了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 收上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.09,0:14:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师 通通做完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.86,0:14:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令 安全索通通解开了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.89,0:15:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你白银
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上让所有人避难
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各区域进行最后检查
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,护身符
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.77,0:15:14.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.68,0:15:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.81,0:15:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在开始S室将成为真空状态
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无限号请前往第七舱门
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.78,0:15:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三输送通道入口开启
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无限号已在舱门待命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有通道关闭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.83,0:15:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有系统正常运作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.96,0:15:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无限号送上发射台
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.68,0:15:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发准备完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始进入倒数
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有十秒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.56,0:16:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8 7 6 5 4 3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无限号 出动！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.95,0:16:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是光太看到的世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.35,0:16:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回避命令？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:35.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.83,0:16:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.83,0:16:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量炮与无限号连结
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.60,0:16:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,锁定目标
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.74,0:16:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,填充能量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.11,0:16:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.38,0:17:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通往目标轨道没有障碍物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上啰 志麻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.72,0:17:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发射！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.91,0:17:31.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.61,0:17:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.91,0:17:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陨石成功被破坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.98,0:17:37.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.42,0:17:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志麻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:45.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碎片就请各位帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.93,0:17:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片…濑？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.33,0:17:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开启所有重力装置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.14,0:17:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装置开启
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备张开力场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备张开力场
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.55,0:18:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形成护罩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,形成护罩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.23,0:18:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上啰 志麻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.38,0:18:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无限号已展开护罩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来就看能够撑多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信那些孩子的运气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.03,0:18:53.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机内温度上升中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在突破35度了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,装置状况？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:18:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然都正常运作中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有几个已经超过负荷极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.80,0:19:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来就是比耐力是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:31.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.64,0:19:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能量波停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.11,0:19:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确认了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二次冲击完全通过
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.98,0:19:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩瀚任务成功了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.32,0:19:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.39,0:19:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了 志麻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很努力嘛 片濑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.73,0:20:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.57,0:20:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火星跟金星圈已恢复通讯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.87,0:20:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两边都平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究极基地也传来消息了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.78,0:20:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边也是全员平安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.08,0:20:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了玲奈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.85,0:20:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢 玲奈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救了世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.63,0:20:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的新人还真不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 是我们大家拯救的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.44,0:20:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我们是幸运的少数」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.87,0:20:46.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我们是雷霆救兵」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是查理五世是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.61,0:20:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是亨利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.15,0:20:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:21:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有点不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过应该是极光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.62,0:21:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.89,0:21:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒 我第一次看到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.79,0:21:08.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然还不知道能不能通
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.40,0:21:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过打电话给志麻看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.57,0:21:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打个电话给姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会接得通吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.64,0:21:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.48,0:21:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳系标准时间西元2356年\N12月19日14时13分
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.45,0:21:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二次冲击通过太阳系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.72,0:21:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类活下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.67,0:21:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有电话进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.17,0:21:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的手机呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.47,0:21:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候还设定接通啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.94,0:21:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 喂？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.18,0:22:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我总是仰望着闪亮的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.78,0:22:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要得到翅膀高飞俯瞰天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.46,0:22:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来无论为何都将来访
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.20,0:22:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期望看到无人曾见的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.80,0:22:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道何谓停止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.04,0:22:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本不安的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.41,0:22:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就任凭自己拥抱它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.05,0:22:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破涕而笑时总会想起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.39,0:22:42.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以活着的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.72,0:22:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类就像是五彩缤纷的繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.23,0:22:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是装饰精美的绮丽夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.01,0:23:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今的我又再次仰望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.01,0:23:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是志麻
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.75,0:23:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是艾丽莎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.55,0:23:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浩瀚任务平安结束
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.02,0:23:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预科课程也进入下一个阶段了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.75,0:23:13.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,训练机的系统也改成DLS了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.55,0:23:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DLS：直达连接系统
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.52,0:23:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接把情报送到脑中\N感觉真是神奇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.26,0:23:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之好像对身体很不好的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.43,0:23:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 难道是会头痛吗
